  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with friends in this chaotic multiplayer hardware store simulator! Build your empire, sabotage competitors' pricing strategies, and handle the mayhem of daily retail operations - all while trying to become the town's premier hardware destination.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/a0d4c4dd0fde79fd190041e5e922a759.avif?t=1745828514\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras_big/a0d4c4dd0fde79fd190041e5e922a759.avif?t=1745828514 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏗️ CHAOS MEETS COMMERCE</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch products tumble as you and your staff race to restock shelves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deal with the physics-based chaos of retail life</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate crowded aisles during flash sales</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frantically reorganize displays to outshine competitors<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/acf8195e0caf2719e008936af380b03c.poster.avif?t=1745828514\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/acf8195e0caf2719e008936af380b03c.webm?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/acf8195e0caf2719e008936af380b03c.mp4?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 TRUE COMPETITIVE MULTIPLAYER</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle up to 3 other players in the same bustling town</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the real impact when competitors undercut your prices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race to stock trending products before your rivals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt your strategy as other players influence the market</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/625acc790e2d5d83afb1da42f30eab9e.poster.avif?t=1745828514\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/625acc790e2d5d83afb1da42f30eab9e.webm?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/625acc790e2d5d83afb1da42f30eab9e.mp4?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📊 DEEP RETAIL WARFARE</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategically price items to steal customers from competitors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monitor rival stores' tactics in real-time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn market events into opportunities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform your store to counter others' specializations<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/92d7f1b864b0bf598ac930a4b4230cfd.poster.avif?t=1745828514\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/92d7f1b864b0bf598ac930a4b4230cfd.webm?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/92d7f1b864b0bf598ac930a4b4230cfd.mp4?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💼 DYNAMIC RETAIL ECOSYSTEM</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a living economy that reacts to all players' actions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch customers choose between competing stores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create price wars that affect everyone's bottom line</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deal with the ripple effects of other players' business decisions<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/a4ad9d4796f75144085935ebd9589242.poster.avif?t=1745828514\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/a4ad9d4796f75144085935ebd9589242.webm?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/a4ad9d4796f75144085935ebd9589242.mp4?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 KEY FEATURES</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based item interactions add unpredictable fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real-time competitive multiplayer for up to 4 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic market affected by all players' decisions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete store design freedom</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep management systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Employee hiring and management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Warehouse logistics<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/cedd01f6c18ee1b1c4df1ac44b537479.poster.avif?t=1745828514\" width=420 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/cedd01f6c18ee1b1c4df1ac44b537479.webm?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358560/extras/cedd01f6c18ee1b1c4df1ac44b537479.mp4?t=1745828514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will your store rise to the top through careful management, or will you embrace the chaos and outmaneuver your rivals? Jump into Hardware Store Simulator and find out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Note: The game supports single-player and multiplayer modes for up to 4 players.</i></p>",
